### 1. TẠO TÀI KHOẢN ADMIN ĐẦU TIÊN (Endpoint này không check Auth lúc vừa init)
### (Lưu ý: Sau khi tạo xong, hãy comment dòng POST này lại để tránh tạo bừa bãi)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/staffs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "staffCode": "EMP001",
  "fullName": "Administrator",
  "username": "admin",
  "passwordHash": "123456",
  "role": "ADMIN",
  "isActive": true
}

### 

### 2. ĐĂNG NHẬP ĐỂ LẤY JWT TOKEN Bearer
# @name loginAdmin
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "123456"
}

### (Lưu biến token vào bộ nhớ tạm của Rest Client)
@authToken = {{loginAdmin.response.body.token}}

### 

### 3. TEST TẠO DANH MỤC (CATEGORY) - CẦN TOKEN ADMIN HOẶC WAREHOUSE_STAFF
POST http://localhost:8080/api/categories
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "name": "Nước Ngọt",
  "slug": "nuoc-ngot",
  "isActive": true
}

###

### 4. LẤY DANH SÁCH CATEGORY (KHÔNG CẦN TRUYỀN TOKEN - Vẫn trả 200)
# (Vì SecurityConfig đang bọc anyRequest().authenticated() nên gọi không token sẽ bị 403 Forbidden)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### 5. TẠO THÊM KHÁCH HÀNG
POST http://localhost:8080/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "customerCode": "CUS001",
  "name": "Khách Vãng Lai",
  "phone": "0987654321",
  "isActive": true
}

###

### 6. UPDATE DRAFT PURCHASE ORDER
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/purchase-orders/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "supplierId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "expectedDate": "2026-03-30",
  "note": "Update draft PO",
  "createdByStaffId": 1,
  "warehouseId": 1,
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": 1,
      "orderedQty": 10,
      "expectedUnitCost": 12000
    }
  ]
}

###

### 7. UPDATE DRAFT GOODS RECEIPT
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/goods-receipts/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "poId": 1,
  "supplierId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "warehouseId": 1,
  "note": "Update draft GR",
  "createdByStaffId": 1,
  "items": [
    {
      "poItemId": 1,
      "productId": 1,
      "receivedQty": 10,
      "unitCost": 12000
    }
  ]
}

###

### 8. UPDATE DRAFT CUSTOMER RETURN
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/customer-returns/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "customerId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "orderId": 1,
  "note": "Update draft customer return",
  "createdByStaffId": 1,
  "warehouseId": 1,
  "items": [
    {
      "orderItemId": 1,
      "productId": 1,
      "qty": 1,
      "refundAmount": 12000
    }
  ]
}

###

### 9. UPDATE DRAFT SUPPLIER RETURN
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/supplier-returns/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "goodsReceiptId": 1,
  "supplierId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "note": "Update draft supplier return",
  "createdByStaffId": 1,
  "warehouseId": 1,
  "items": [
    {
      "goodsReceiptItemId": 1,
      "productId": 1,
      "qty": 1,
      "returnAmount": 12000,
      "note": "Loi vo"
    }
  ]
}

###

### 10. UPDATE DRAFT STOCK ADJUSTMENT
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/stock-adjustments/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "warehouseId": 1,
  "reason": "Cycle count",
  "note": "Update draft adjustment",
  "createdByStaffId": 1,
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": 1,
      "actualQty": 100
    }
  ]
}

###

### 11. CREATE ORDER - STATUS SHOULD BE POSTED
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "warehouseId": 1,
  "paymentMethod": "CASH",
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": 1,
      "quantity": 1,
      "salePrice": 15000
    }
  ]
}

###

### 12. PREVIEW COUPON (backend tự tính giảm giá)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/coupon-preview?couponCode=KHAIMUA2026&grossAmount=590000
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### 13. CREATE ORDER WITH COUPON (frontend chỉ gửi couponCode)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "warehouseId": 1,
  "discountAmount": 0,
  "couponCode": "KHAIMUA2026",
  "surchargeAmount": 0,
  "paymentMethod": "CASH",
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": 1,
      "quantity": 2,
      "salePrice": 295000
    }
  ]
}
